stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_parse_request: parse List[DataColumnsByRootIdentifier]
    q_parse_request --> q_compute_min_epoch: minimum_request_epoch = max(current_epoch - MIN_EPOCHS, FULU_FORK_EPOCH)
    q_compute_min_epoch --> q_check_total: requested_columns_count = sum(len(r.columns) for r in request)
    q_check_total --> q_reject_too_many: requested_columns_count > MAX_REQUEST_DATA_COLUMN_SIDECARS
    q_check_total --> q_iter_identifiers: requested_columns_count <= MAX_REQUEST_DATA_COLUMN_SIDECARS
    q_reject_too_many --> [*]: reject request
    q_iter_identifiers --> q_check_epoch: for identifier in request
    q_check_epoch --> q_skip_old: block epoch < minimum_request_epoch
    q_check_epoch --> q_lookup_block: block epoch >= minimum_request_epoch
    q_skip_old --> q_iter_identifiers: ResourceUnavailable or skip
    q_lookup_block --> q_check_gossip_valid: block passes gossip validation
    q_check_gossip_valid --> q_skip_invalid: block fails gossip validation
    q_check_gossip_valid --> q_iter_columns: block valid
    q_skip_invalid --> q_iter_identifiers: skip block
    q_iter_columns --> q_send_sidecar: for column_index in identifier.columns
    q_send_sidecar --> q_send_chunk: send DataColumnSidecar response_chunk
    q_send_chunk --> q_iter_columns: more columns
    q_iter_columns --> q_iter_identifiers: all columns for block sent
    q_iter_identifiers --> [*]: all identifiers processed
